mods.abstract: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing the Old Timey Gospel Sing with Wendy Johnson and the Massagers and the Kenny Parker Trio at the Erwin High School Auditorium on November 9. Poster features metal photoplates of Wendy Johnson and the Messengers and the Kenny Parker Trio. For additional information about this poster see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/27337.
